items.name: Tripple Dipper
items.description: Why choose one when you can choose three? Select three appetizers and enjoy! Served with dipping sauces.

items.name: Southwestern Eggrolls
items.description: These aren’t your ordinary eggrolls. Crispy flour tortillas, chicken, black beans, corn, jalapeño Jack cheese, red peppers, spinach. Served with avocado-ranch.

items.name: Skillet Queso
items.description: Your chip’s favorite dip for over 25 years. Original with beef. Served with chips & salsa.

items.name: Fried Pickles
items.description: Served with house-made ranch.

items.name: Queso Burger
items.description: This half-pound patty comes smothered in white queso, crunchy tortilla strips & pico.

items.name: Mushroom Swiss Burger
items.description: There’s so mush-room in our hearts for this one. Topped with sauteed onions, mushrooms, Swiss, lettuce, tomato & garlic aioli.

items.name: Southern Smokehouse Burger
items.description: Bacon, cheddar, pickles, Awesome Blossom Petals, lettuce, tomato, garlic aioli. Served with a side of original BBQ sauce.

items.name: Carnitas Fajitas
items.description: Pulled pork carnitas, grilled bell peppers & onions. Topped with a drizzle of mango-habanero sauce and green onions.

items.name: Mushroom Jack Chicken Fajitas
items.description: Grilled chicken, sauteed mushrooms, crumbled bacon & mixed cheese.

items.name: Black Bean & Veggie Fajitas
items.description: Black bean patty, roasted asparagus, sauteed mushrooms, corn & black bean salsa, queso fresco, avocado & a drizzle of spicy Santa Fe sauce.

items.name: Cajun Chicken Pasta
items.description: Grilled chicken, penne in Alfredo sauce, topped with chile spices, Parmesan, tomatoes, green onions. Served with garlic toast.

items.name: Cajun Shrimp Pasta
items.description: Shrimp, penne in Alfredo sauce, topped with chile spices, Parmesan, tomatoes, green onions. Served with garlic toast.

items.name: Chipotle Chicken Fresh Mex Bowl
items.description: Grilled chicken, pico, field greens, Mexican rice, corn & black bean salsa, avocado, shredded cheese, tortilla strips, cilantro, chipotle pesto, house-made ranch.

items.name: Chipotle Shrimp Fresh Mex Bowl
items.description: Shrimp, pico, field greens, Mexican rice, corn & black bean salsa, avocado, shredded cheese, tortilla strips, cilantro, chipotle pesto, house-made ranch.

items.name: Spicy Shrimp Tacos
items.description: Three spicy chile-lime shrimp tacos in flour tortillas with pico, avocado, cilantro, coleslaw queso fresco. Served with Mexican rice & black beans.

items.name: Ancho Salmon
items.description: Seared chile-rubbed Atlantic salmon, spicy citrus-chile sauce, cilantro, queso fresco. Served with Mexican rice & steamed broccoli.

items.name: Crispy Chicken Crispers
items.description: Served with fries, corn on the cob and choice of honey-mustard, BBQ sauce or house-made ranch.

items.name: Crispy Honey-Chipotle Chicken Crispers
items.description: Served with fries, corn on the cob and ranch.

items.name: Honey-Chipotle Crispers® & Waffles
items.description: Crispers on top of Belgian waffles. Topped with bacon, jalapeños, ancho-chile ranch. Served with fries & honey-chipotle sauce.

items.name: Crispy Buffalo Bleu Crispers
items.description: Served with fries, corn on the cob and bleu cheese.

items.name: Crispy Mango-Habanero Crispers
items.description: Served with fries, corn on the cob and ranch.
